# car-management-service

1. POST Create-Car  http://{localhost}:{port}/cars
   Request

{
	"name": "Corolla",
	"description":"Toyota Corolla",
	"category_ids": [1],                        #list of category id
	"tag_ids":[1],                              #list of tag id
    "color": "Black",
	"images": ["data:image/jpeg;base64,"]
	
}

   Response
{
    "name": "Corolla",
    "engineNumber": "00202",
    "categories": [
        {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "sedan"
        }
    ],
    "tags": [
        {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "v3"
        }
    ],
    "images": {
        "0098": "data:image/jpeg;base64,"
    },
    "description": "Toyota Corolla"
}
